article_title: Palestinian Red Crescent says five people have been killed in bombing on headquarters.
sentence: The  Palestinian  Red  Crescent  Society  says  five  people  have  been  killed  and  three  injured  in  Israeli  bombing  on  its  headquarters  in  Khan  Younis,  a  city  in  the  south  of  the  Gaza  Strip.
